# Internal security tracking — must NOT be committed (lists potential
# vulnerabilities and proposed fixes; sharing publicly = leaking attack
# surface). Each finding gets a dedicated commit when fixed.
SECURITY_FINDINGS.md

# Internal test-infrastructure tracking — flake patterns, port
# collisions, parallelism issues. Not security-sensitive but tracked
# locally to avoid noise in git history until a fix lands.
TEST_INFRA_FINDINGS.md
